02:14.635 --> 02:17.930
One moment he was well
and then he collapsed, and...

02:18.264 --> 02:19.724
It was terrible.

02:25.896 --> 02:27.314
I can't believe this.

02:27.481 --> 02:29.233
Thank God, you've recovered!

02:30.901 --> 02:33.279
We were so scared
to lose the both of you.

02:55.968 --> 02:58.095
Hail and farewell, my brother.

03:00.890 --> 03:02.641
Hail and farewell.

