Ketill, my friend.

04:14.338 --> 04:15.714
Come.

04:16.841 --> 04:19.635
Come. You see how I am?
Come, let me thank you.

04:21.470 --> 04:22.930
Oh, thank the gods!

04:23.848 --> 04:25.432
You have saved us.

04:26.517 --> 04:28.769
