to celebrate with.

04:51.625 --> 04:53.002
Oh, we do.

04:55.921 --> 04:57.590
So let's celebrate.

05:09.893 --> 05:11.186
Thank you.

05:33.626 --> 05:35.002
Make way.

05:54.938 --> 05:56.273
My people.

05:56.857 --> 05:59.193
You are all welcome
to the Thing.

06:00.569 --> 06:01.695
It is important to us

06:01.779 --> 06:04.114
that everyone here
feels involved

06:04.198 --> 06:05.824
in the life of our great town.

06:06.450 --> 06:07.743
Kattegat is grown.

06:07.951 --> 06:09.662
It is now a huge
trading station.

06:09.995 --> 06:13.290
The greatest trading station
in Scandinavia.

06:14.708 --> 06:17.252
Kattegat has changed
since my father's time.

06:18.879 --> 06:20.923
In those days, he knew everyone

06:21.256 --> 06:23.550
and he was happy
to share his power

06:23.634 --> 06:25.803
with those he knew
and trusted, of course.

06:28.305 --> 06:32.351
My father gave me
this responsibility

06:32.434 --> 06:36.438
and our father, Odin,
gave me this responsibility.

06:36.522 --> 06:39.233
I've accepted it,
and I ask you to trust me.

06:41.026 --> 06:44.071
We cannot allow everyone to vote

06:44.154 --> 06:46.740
on everything
which affects our kingdom.

06:46.865 --> 06:50.828
We have a duty to protect it.
I have a duty to protect it.

06:58.877 --> 07:02.881
So, we have to change the rules.

07:13.892 --> 07:15.394
What are you doing?

07:15.477 --> 07:17.229
Packing your things, my dear.

07:17.312 --> 07:19.690
Your husband is dead, you've
no reason to remain here,

07:19.773 --> 07:22.276
unless of course,
you are with child.

07:25.320 --> 07:26.739
Otherwise you must return home

07:26.822 --> 07:28.741
to your mother,
I really am very sorry.

07:29.783 --> 07:31.910
I don't think
you're sorry at all.

07:31.994 --> 07:34.413
I think that you control
everything that happens here.

07:35.831 --> 07:37.124
If only that were true.

07:38.167 --> 07:42.504
You don't seem very sorry that my
husband and your son died so suddenly.

07:43.422 --> 07:45.090
And I don't know
what to make of that.

07:46.300 --> 07:51.138
You don't need to make anything
of that, my dear child.

07:52.181 --> 07:53.974
Life is complicated enough,

07:54.057 --> 07:57.060
and you are young enough
to find another husband.

08:00.355 --> 08:02.941
Well, then I hope his mother
is nothing like you.

08:04.359 --> 08:07.237
My dear, he should be so lucky.

08:11.325 --> 08:15.204
People I trust,
will vote on land issues,

08:15.287 --> 08:19.041
matrimonial matters,
murder inquiries.

08:19.124 --> 08:21.043
Things that you do not need
to worry about.

08:22.169 --> 08:24.129
Because I will take care of you.

08:24.546 --> 08:26.048
I will lead you!

08:26.632 --> 08:30.010
Now, what is truly important
is to know who we are

08:30.260 --> 08:33.847
and who is with us
and who is against us.

08:33.931 --> 08:36.683
And we know who
we are, don't we?

08:36.767 --> 08:38.227
Yeah!

08:38.310 --> 08:39.645
Yes, we do.

08:39.728 --> 08:42.439
So, now, it is time
to find out those

08:42.523 --> 08:45.192
who threaten us,
who is against us.

08:47.820 --> 08:49.238
Maybe it is your neighbor.

08:52.282 --> 08:54.034
Perhaps it is someone you know.

08:54.660 --> 08:55.869
A family member.

08:57.621 --> 08:58.914
A brother.

09:01.041 --> 09:02.042
A son.

09:04.211 --> 09:05.838
They talk about me.

09:06.004 --> 09:08.841
They whisper
that I am the enemy.

09:11.051 --> 09:14.054
But, of course,
they are the enemy.

09:14.680 --> 09:17.015
They want to destroy
our kingdom.

09:17.099 --> 09:20.060
They want to encourage
our enemies to attack us

09:20.143 --> 09:22.646
and invade us.
Is that what you want?

09:22.729 --> 09:23.730
No!

09:23.814 --> 09:25.440
Do you want me to protect you?

09:25.524 --> 09:26.525
Yes.

09:26.608 --> 09:27.836
Do you want me to destroy them?

09:27.860 --> 09:28.861
Yes!

09:29.403 --> 09:30.404
Yes!

09:31.905 --> 09:32.906
Yes!

09:33.574 --> 09:35.492
Destroy them.

09:35.576 --> 09:36.577
Yes.

09:40.414 --> 09:45.043
Ivar, the Boneless!
Ivar, the Boneless!

09:56.555 --> 09:58.015
Why is Elsewith not here?

09:59.391 --> 10:00.851
And Ethelfled?

10:01.351 --> 10:03.979
I thought we should talk.
You and I.

10:04.897 --> 10:07.316
It's not been easy
since you fell sick.

10:07.399 --> 10:09.067
I had to deal with the traitors.

10:10.110 --> 10:11.945
They were still
plotting against you.

10:13.113 --> 10:14.406
Perhaps they still are.

10:20.078 --> 10:21.079
And...

10:22.581 --> 10:23.999
I had to deal with your brother.

10:26.585 --> 10:27.586
My brother?

10:29.838 --> 10:31.465
What exactly does that mean?

10:33.967 --> 10:34.968
It means...

10:37.554 --> 10:39.848
His death wasn't natural.

10:47.856 --> 10:49.274
You had better explain.

10:50.651 --> 10:51.652
And quickly.

10:51.902 --> 10:55.781
He had plotted against you
before, Alfred, he told me.

10:56.615 --> 10:57.616
He confessed.

10:58.909 --> 11:01.244
And then he said he would
never plot against you again,

11:01.328 --> 11:04.122
but I satisfied myself
he was lying.

11:05.916 --> 11:10.879
I knew, as long as he was
alive, he would do anything.

11:12.089 --> 11:15.676
Join any plot, any conspiracy

11:15.759 --> 11:18.053
that promised to make him king.

11:22.849 --> 11:25.727
He thought you had usurped him,

11:25.811 --> 11:28.814
and he could never,
ever forgive you.

11:32.901 --> 11:33.902
So?

11:39.116 --> 11:40.450
I poisoned him.

11:42.703 --> 11:45.497
I killed one of my sons

11:47.124 --> 11:48.458
to save the other.

11:51.795 --> 11:53.547
May God forgive me.

12:37.090 --> 12:38.800
Can we talk now?

12:40.969 --> 12:43.722
You've awoken from along sleep

12:43.805 --> 12:46.475
and seemed to have forgotten
that you're a king.

12:47.517 --> 12:51.188
You are behaving as if you
were an ordinary person.

12:51.855 --> 12:55.609
You grieve as if you were
an ordinary person.

12:55.692 --> 12:57.861
You show your feelings

12:57.944 --> 13:00.489
as if you were
an ordinary person,

13:00.572 --> 13:01.948
but all of that must stop.

13:05.952 --> 13:11.083
A king cannot be like
an ordinary person,

13:13.168 --> 13:18.131
must not behave orhavefeenngs
like an ordinary person.

13:19.132 --> 13:23.887
A king must be prepared to
do the most terrible things.

13:24.679 --> 13:27.182
Things against all conscience,

13:28.767 --> 13:31.978
if he wants to survive.

15:01.109 --> 15:02.235
You saw them?

15:03.028 --> 15:04.070
