of my own brother,

15:21.838 --> 15:24.674
then who else
will dare stand against me?

15:27.177 --> 15:29.512
I think that would be a mistake.

15:35.560 --> 15:36.561
Why?

15:38.021 --> 15:39.481
<i>Nat, you are a god.</i>

15:41.024 --> 15:42.234
