15:42.317 --> 15:45.070
will always be more popular
among the common people

15:45.153 --> 15:47.197
than a vengeful god, like Odin.

15:52.744 --> 15:56.289
Wouldn't you rather beloved,
than feared?

16:03.171 --> 16:04.547
I don't know.

16:08.718 --> 16:10.011
I'm not sure.

16:44.713 --> 16:46.131
Why aren't you getting ready?

16:47.007 --> 16:48.133
We have to leave.

16:51.928 --> 16:54.472
Yes, Floki, we are ready.

16:58.393 --> 16:59.769
Come on, you old witch.

17:00.186 --> 17:02.897
What? Why did you say that?

17:03.481 --> 17:06.860
