a witch and a murderess.

17:07.444 --> 17:09.195
And you deserve to die!

17:09.779 --> 17:11.906
- What are you doing?
- Mother!

17:14.117 --> 17:15.994
- Stop!
- Don't you worry, Floki.

17:16.077 --> 17:19.247
