such an empty and idle life.

19:31.754 --> 19:33.882
After all, you are my brother
and I love you.

19:35.216 --> 19:38.428
So, how could
I make myself useful?

19:40.221 --> 19:41.598
You could leave Kattegat.

19:45.435 --> 19:49.939
Go on a diplomatic trip to the Great
Hall of King Olaf, the Stout.

19:50.356 --> 19:51.774
You will cement our alliance,

19:51.858 --> 19:55.069
help him prepare for our springtime
attacks on York and Wessex.

19:55.153 --> 19:56.863
