19:58.031 --> 19:59.449
I don't want to leave Kattegat.

20:04.996 --> 20:06.831
I'm afraid you cannot refuse.

20:10.126 --> 20:11.377
What is your name?

20:12.670 --> 20:14.672
There.
There!

20:17.050 --> 20:20.011
My brother has been remiss
in not introducing us.

20:22.263 --> 20:23.806
He seems very fond of you.

20:24.349 --> 20:25.808
We love each other.

20:26.684 --> 20:27.936
Hmm.

20:29.437 --> 20:30.605
That is good.

20:31.814 --> 20:33.066
That is good, Hvitserk.

20:34.692 --> 20:36.903
It would be a pity
if I had to burn her alive.

20:37.362 --> 20:39.697
You wouldn't do that, brother.

20:41.199 --> 20:42.367
Now, would you?

20:47.538 --> 20:48.706
No.

20:49.415 --> 20:50.792
No, I wouldn't...

20:52.752 --> 20:55.588
