21:38.631 --> 21:39.841
Don't snivel.

21:41.050 --> 21:42.593
What difference does it make?

21:44.012 --> 21:46.764
We're all just meat.

21:50.518 --> 21:52.061
It all goes to nothing.

22:02.363 --> 22:03.656
I don't understand.

22:04.949 --> 22:06.242
Of course you do.

22:06.868 --> 22:08.828
