believing again, Ketill.

22:24.510 --> 22:26.054
We are what we are, Floki.

22:26.971 --> 22:28.431
And the gods have made us so.

22:34.228 --> 22:35.897
You can't kill Helgi.

22:38.983 --> 22:40.360
None of this is his fault.

22:42.779 --> 22:45.823
He loved your daughter,
and he's a good man.

22:47.867 --> 22:48.993
Spare him, at least.

22:52.580 --> 22:53.915
Maybe I Will, Floki.

22:56.542 --> 22:58.211
If Helgi is still alive
in the morning,

22:58.294 --> 22:59.879
