we will have safe passage.

24:57.205 --> 24:58.748
How can you be so sure?

24:59.540 --> 25:00.666
My father told me.

25:02.543 --> 25:03.586
Your father?

25:05.129 --> 25:06.923
You mean Ragnar?
Ragnar told you?

25:07.215 --> 25:08.925
Yes. He spoke to me
in a dream.

25:10.343 --> 25:12.470
Ah, finally, a proper fight!

25:15.181 --> 25:16.599
Don't you ever dream?

25:22.522 --> 25:24.273
Yeah!

25:30.363 --> 25:33.741
Your father loved Ivar,
everyone knows that.

25:33.824 --> 25:35.826
<i>He chose Nat.
He chose me.</i>

25:37.328 --> 25:38.871
I'm his eldest son.

25:39.997 --> 25:41.374
