of my intended wife Gunnhild.

26:17.535 --> 26:18.911
Fight me, you weak men!

26:19.078 --> 26:21.163
She must agree
and swear to the gods

26:21.247 --> 26:22.999
that once I die,
you will become king.

26:26.502 --> 26:27.980
Whether or not
she'll want to marry you

26:28.004 --> 26:30.631
will be of no further
consequence to me.

26:30.756 --> 26:31.799
