About 2,000.

31:05.948 --> 31:08.367
The Danes will have
1,000 more warriors.

31:09.034 --> 31:12.705
I will ride myself with the head
of the army to inspire our forces.

31:12.788 --> 31:15.249
I also believe that
I have some good commanders.

31:15.332 --> 31:16.542
The Danes won't be frightened

31:16.625 --> 31:18.065
to see you
with the head of the army.

31:18.252 --> 31:20.629
Believe me.
And why do you say that?

31:24.800 --> 31:26.844
I have a terrible habit
of telling the truth.

31:33.892 --> 31:36.687
Very well.
Then what do you advise?

31:37.813 --> 31:39.690
I advise you make me
the head of your army.

31:41.567 --> 31:43.360
I think you should listen to me.

31:43.444 --> 31:45.487
Words are fine,
but they don't win battles.

31:47.031 --> 31:49.116
If you make me
the head of the army,

31:49.366 --> 31:51.410
I will find a way
of dealing with the Danes.

31:52.911 --> 31:54.747
Otherwise, you have no hope.

32:17.936 --> 32:19.605
Why do you sneak up on me?

32:20.981 --> 32:22.483
Why do you stay in the shadows?

32:23.567 --> 32:24.860
You're a king.

32:28.197 --> 32:29.490
What do you want to say?

32:31.408 --> 32:32.409
<i>Must, um...</i>

32:34.203 --> 32:35.245
Wanted to remind you

32:35.329 --> 32:37.706
that fate has
brought us together.

32:44.922 --> 32:46.715
You yourself said as much...

32:49.677 --> 32:51.303
While you were still married.

32:52.888 --> 32:56.558
I said I knew my life was going to change.
And so it has.

33:00.938 --> 33:02.648
I'm no longer the person I was.

33:05.526 --> 33:07.111
We're always the same.

33:08.737 --> 33:10.239
We just pretend to change.

33:14.660 --> 33:17.496
I see that Bjorn Ironside
has claimed you.

33:19.581 --> 33:20.916
You're mistaken.

33:21.333 --> 33:22.710
No man will ever claim me.

33:25.129 --> 33:29.883
I prefer it to think that the
gods have you and me in mind.

33:31.093 --> 33:32.553
I don't know about the gods.

33:40.811 --> 33:42.354
What do you have in mind then?

33:44.523 --> 33:46.817
Do you still want
to be king of all Norway?

33:48.861 --> 33:50.696
My ambition has never changed.

33:56.034 --> 33:57.035
Well, then...

33:58.704 --> 33:59.997
I shall like to be queen.

34:25.355 --> 34:28.192
My Lady?
What were you doing?

34:29.943 --> 34:31.069
Doesn't matter.

34:33.614 --> 34:34.865
Really doesn't matter.

34:52.674 --> 34:53.675
Father!

34:55.511 --> 34:56.512
Father!

35:30.671 --> 35:31.755
What happened?

35:33.257 --> 35:34.299
Floki?

35:35.300 --> 35:36.552
Tell me what happened.

35:38.011 --> 35:39.137
Take this.

35:40.097 --> 35:41.139
Floki.

35:43.976 --> 35:45.102
They killed them all.

35:47.104 --> 35:48.188
All of them.

35:49.064 --> 35:52.901
Your father and your brother,
they killed them all.

35:55.487 --> 35:56.989
They wanted revenge.

35:57.114 --> 35:59.658
No. And they had
planned it a long time.

36:01.034 --> 36:03.245
No!
I couldn't stop them.

36:05.414 --> 36:06.582
No.

36:08.375 --> 36:09.626
I can't believe it.

36:11.962 --> 36:13.672
What about Helgi?

36:14.298 --> 36:18.135
No, please, surely they couldn't
have killed him. Please.

36:19.970 --> 36:21.054
All of them.

36:21.847 --> 36:23.640
No!
Helgi. too.

36:24.725 --> 36:27.728
I pleaded with them. I asked
your father to spare him, but...

36:29.229 --> 36:30.397
No.

36:30.939 --> 36:32.649
No!
I'm sorry. Aud.

36:33.483 --> 36:34.484
I'm sorry.

36:35.861 --> 36:38.572
Please. no. They couldn't have.
I'm sorry.

36:40.741 --> 36:42.826
I should never have brought
you all to this place.

36:58.508 --> 37:00.552
You didn't even really
see the gods, did you?

37:17.945 --> 37:20.614
When you come back,
we should get married.

37:20.739 --> 37:23.075
Yes. We will have
lots of children.

37:23.700 --> 37:27.287
You won't be idle anymore. Oh. I
won't be idle. even before that.

37:27.996 --> 37:29.122
Believe me.

37:30.290 --> 37:32.751
What do you mean?
You scare me.

37:35.629 --> 37:37.422
It means that
I've come to a decision.

37:38.215 --> 37:42.135
It has taken along time, but I
know it's the right choice.

37:42.219 --> 37:44.763
What have you decided?
Tell me, please.

37:44.846 --> 37:47.057
I can't tell you,
it will be too dangerous.

37:53.313 --> 37:54.356
Farewell, my love.

37:54.773 --> 37:56.900
And be careful. Yes?
Mmm-hmm.

37:56.984 --> 37:58.527
Be careful of my brother.

38:52.831 --> 38:54.416
King Harald is in love with you.

38:56.501 --> 38:57.544
I know.

39:01.131 --> 39:02.215
Did he tell you?

39:03.592 --> 39:04.593
Yes.

39:05.552 --> 39:07.929
He has told me that we are
fated to be together.

39:08.555 --> 39:09.681
Mmm.

39:11.516 --> 39:13.101
Do you really believe that?

39:15.020 --> 39:17.689
Who knows our fate? Do you?

39:22.277 --> 39:24.321
He still wants
to be king of Norway.

39:25.572 --> 39:26.615
Ah.

39:27.741 --> 39:30.577
And it seems he puts
the highest value on love...

39:32.078 --> 39:34.539
He is a man who always
wants to be in love.

39:37.626 --> 39:39.252
I would like to have his heart.

39:40.754 --> 39:42.005
Instead of mine.

39:43.256 --> 39:44.299
Why do you say that?

39:45.300 --> 39:46.426
Well, I've had many women.

39:47.677 --> 39:49.721
But I'm not sure
I've ever been in love.

39:52.015 --> 39:54.935
And you are not in love with me?
I don't know.

39:57.103 --> 39:58.772
I think about you all the time.

40:02.526 --> 40:04.166
And then I'm thinking
about something else

40:04.194 --> 40:05.421
and then
I think about you again.

40:05.445 --> 40:06.780
And it happens day and night.

40:08.448 --> 40:09.783
Why are you telling me this?

40:11.117 --> 40:12.702
I don't know,
perhaps I'm in love.

40:18.083 --> 40:19.417
What if you don't love me?

40:20.961 --> 40:22.420
What if you love King Harald?

40:22.504 --> 40:24.130
He can make you
the queen of Norway.

40:25.465 --> 40:26.883
I suppose he could try.

40:34.349 --> 40:36.726
I'm afraid.

40:40.313 --> 40:42.399
I'm afraid to ask you
if you love me.

40:44.401 --> 40:46.611
You are one of the most
famous men in the world.

40:47.863 --> 40:49.114
And you're afraid of me?

40:52.993 --> 40:54.327
I'm alone.

40:57.497 --> 40:59.165
Alone, naked and afraid.

41:03.879 --> 41:05.213
You know something?

41:07.257 --> 41:09.092
I respect you even more
for saying that.

41:12.888 --> 41:17.183
And I will take your words and lock
them away in my heart forever.

41:38.538 --> 41:39.831
Say it.

41:43.793 --> 41:45.086
Say it.

41:50.508 --> 41:51.760
Say it.

41:55.388 --> 41:56.640
Say it.

42:03.313 --> 42:05.732
I love you.

43:40.869 --> 43:42.454
Aud!

44:03.683 --> 44:05.685
No! No!
